a:17:{s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";s:11:"small_descr";s:159:"Rumalaya liniment is a polyherbal formulation indicated for the management of pain and inflammation associated with the musculoskeletal inflammatory disorders.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:205:"Rumalaya liniment ist ein pflanzliches Präparat, das aus mehreren verschiedenen Kräuter besteht. Es dient der Leitung von Schmerzen und Entzündungen, die mit Muskel-Skelett-Erkrankungen verbunden sind. ";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:173:"Rumalaya Liniment est une formulation polyherbacée indiquée pour le contrôle de la douleur et l'inflammation associées aux troubles musculo-squelettiques inflammatoires.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:181:"Rumalaya liniment es una formulación poliherbácea indicada para el tratamiento del dolor y la inflamación asociados con las enfermedades inflamatorias musculosas y esqueléticas.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:166:"Rumalaya liniment è una formulazione di molte erbe indicata per la terapia del dolore e dell'infiammazione associati con i disordini infiammatori muscoloscheletrici.";s:10:"full_descr";s:2570:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Rumalaya liniment is a polyherbal formulation indicated for the management of pain and inflammation associated with the musculoskeletal inflammatory disorders.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Please consult your physician to prescribe the dosage that bestsuits you.</p><p>Rumalaya liniment spreads easily, ensures deeper penetration and exerts analgesic, anti-inflammatory, and rubefacient actions.&nbsp;<br />Gandhapura taila (oil of Gaultheria) and Sarala (Indian turpentine), the prominent ingredients of Rumalaya liniment, have well known analgesic actions.&nbsp;<br />The anti-inflammatory effect of Rumalaya liniment reduces inflammation and swelling associated with pain.&nbsp;<br />The rubefacient action of Rumalaya liniment helps flush out the chemical mediators of pain and inflammation, and help in faster relief.</p><p>Clean the affected area. Pour sufficient quantity of Rumalaya liniment and massage gently till the liniment is absorbed. Apply two to three times daily, or as directed by your physician.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Use it as prescribed by your doctor.</p><p>If you miss a dose of Rumalaya liniment and you are using it regularly, use it as soon as possible. Do not use 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>STORAGE&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p><strong>MORE INFO:</strong><br /><br />Active Ingredients:&nbsp;Gandhapura taila (oil of Gaultheria) and Sarala (Indian turpentine)</p><p>Gandhapura taila (oil of Gaultheria) and Sarala (Indian turpentine), the prominent ingredients of Rumalaya liniment, have well known analgesic actions. <br /><br /> The anti-inflammatory effect of Rumalaya liniment reduces inflammation and swelling associated with pain.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>Rumalaya liniment should not be applied to open lesions or wounds. Avoid contact with eyes and mucous membranes.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>Rumalaya liniment is not known to have any side effects if applied as per the prescribed directions for use. <br /><br /><strong>More Information</strong><br /><br />Indications:</p><p>Arthralgia</p><p>Sprains &amp; strains</p><p>Arthritic conditions including osteoarthritis, gout, frozen shoulder, etc.</p><p>Cervical and lumbar spondylitis</p><p>Low backache</p><p>Painful/traumatic inflammatory conditions like fibrositis, bursitis, synovitis, capsulitis, tenosynovitis, myositis, and sciatica</p><p>Sports injuries</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:6:"22.425";s:9:"pack_name";s:7:"bottles";s:4:"type";s:2:"ml";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:60;a:10:{i:5891;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5891";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:4:"34.5";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5892;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5892";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"27.79167";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5893;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5893";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.55556";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5894;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5894";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"24.4375";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5895;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5895";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"23.76667";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5896;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5896";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"23.31944";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5897;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5897";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:2:"23";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5898;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5898";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.76042";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5899;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5899";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.57407";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}i:5900;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5900";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:6:"22.425";s:4:"name";s:17:"Rumalaya liniment";}}}}